## List Watchlist items [/watchlist/items{?apikey,limit,offset,append_to_response,filter_genre,sort,order,unified,filter_score_min,filter_score_max}]

#### ðŸ“„ Pagination

Fetches watchlist items. Use `append_to_response=genre,poster` to include genres and posters in the response. To filter results by a specific genre, use `filter_genre=fantasy` to retrieve only fantasy items.
Returns a `pagination` block alongside the data, mirroring the sync collection response format.

#### â­ Supporter Feature: Rating Filters

Supporters can filter watchlist items by rating thresholds. See the complete list of available rating filters in the `/lists/{listid}/items` endpoint documentation.

By default, items are sorted by date added.

+ Parameters
    + limit: 100 (integer, optional)
    + offset: 10 (integer, optional)
    + append_to_response: `genre,poster` (string, optional) - Additional information to append.
    + filter_genre: `fantasy` (string, optional) - Filter by genre, works if genre is included.
    + filter_score_min: 70 (integer, optional) - â­ Supporter only. Filter by minimum MDBList score (0-100).
    + filter_score_max: 90 (integer, optional) - â­ Supporter only. Filter by maximum MDBList score (0-100).
    + sort: `score` (string, optional)
        + Members
            + `score`
            + `score_average`
            + `released`
            + `releasedigital`
            + `imdbrating`
            + `imdbvotes`
            + `last_air_date`
            + `imdbpopular`
            + `tmdbpopular`
            + `rogerebert`
